OL,6,FCraig and Lindsay Foreman were
OL,7,Freportedly detained in January but
OL,8,FIran's state-run media revealed this
OL,9,Fweek they had been accused of security-
OL,10,Frelated offences.
OL,12,FThe couple were ultimately heading for
OL,13,FAustralia, having crossed into Iran
OL,14,Ffrom Armenia on December 30.
OL,16,FMrs Foreman was reportedly conducting
OL,17,Fa research project during the journey,
OL,18,Fasking people what makes a "good life".
