OL,6,FShe had reportedly planned to present
OL,7,Fher findings at a positive psychology
OL,8,Fconference in Brisbane in July.
OL,10,FThe couple had shared a number of
OL,11,Fupdates from Iran and had been
OL,12,Fplanning to enter Pakistan next.
OL,14,F"To put your minds at rest, we are
OL,15,Fhaving the most amazing time in Iran,"
