OL,6,F"We would like to take this
OL,7,Fopportunity to address the distressing
OL,8,Fsituation concerning Craig and Lindsay
OL,9,FForeman who are currently being
OL,10,Fdetained in Kerman, Iran," the
OL,11,Fstatement read.
OL,13,F"This unexpected turn of events has
OL,14,Fcaused significant concern for our
OL,15,Fentire family, and we are deeply
OL,16,Ffocused on ensuring their safety and
OL,17,Fwell-being during this trying time.
